title: PML Salik Hussain wins PP-32 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Chaudhry Salik Hussain has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-32 Gujrat-VI by securing 55,615 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Chaudhary Pervez Elahi, independent candidate, who bagged 44,713 votes.
Votersâ€™ turn- out remained 41%.
